```dockerfile
# Build stage
FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:resolve

COPY src ./src
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

# Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

# Install required packages
RUN apk add --no-cache \
    curl \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu \
    ca-certificates

# Create app user
RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -D -u 1001 -G app app

# Set working directory
WORKDIR /app

# Import AWS RDS root CA certificates
RUN curl -o /tmp/rds-ca-2019-root.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-2019-root.pem && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca-2019-root -file /tmp/rds-ca-2019-root.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/rds-ca-2019-root.pem

RUN curl -o /tmp/rds-ca-2024-root.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-2024-root.pem && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca-2024-root -file /tmp/rds-ca-2024-root.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/rds-ca-2024-root.pem

# Import Azure DigiCert certificate
RUN curl -o /tmp/digicert.pem https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt && \
    keytool -import -alias azure-digicert -file /tmp/digicert.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/digicert.pem

# Copy JAR from builder
COPY --from=builder /build/target/*.jar /app/app.jar

# Change ownership to app user
RUN chown -R app:app /app

# Switch to non-root user
USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=40s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

ENTRYPOINT ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
